ntherefore do not expect the properties of the stars that formed from this\ncollapsed gas to depend on the value of the streaming velocity. The spin and\nshape of this central gas clump are uncorrelated with the same properties\nmeasured on the scale of the halo as a whole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Jun 2019 10:44:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2020 03:23:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-07"}
