ngle-q helical structure in contrast to metallic SrFeO3 that hosts\nmulti-q structures. Our results provide important insight into the role of\nelectron itinerancy in the formation of multi-q spin structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Jun 2019 14:40:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
